{"id": "art-8", "label": "Art. 8", "title": "Art. 8", "slug": "art-8", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 8 </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>Actul\nconstitutiv al <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> pe <span\nclass=SpellE>ac&#355;iuni</span> sau în comandit&#259; pe <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iuni</span>\nva cuprinde:</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_661813412\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2536\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_661813412\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)datele de identificare a fondatorilor; la societatea în\ncomandit&#259; pe <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iuni</span> vor fi <span\nclass=SpellE>men&#355;iona&#355;i</span> <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>asocia&#355;ii</span> <span class=SpellE>comandita&#355;i</span>;</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_808768434\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2535\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_808768434\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)forma, denumirea <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> sediul\nsocial;</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>c)obiectul\nde activitate al <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>, cu precizarea\ndomeniului <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> a <span class=SpellE>activit&#259;&#355;ii</span>\nprincipale;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1319831675\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2534\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1319831675\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>d)capitalul social subscris <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\ncel v&#259;rsat <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>, în cazul în care societatea\nare un capital autorizat, cuantumul acestuia;</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1462555030\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2533\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1462555030\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>e)natura <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> valoarea\nbunurilor constituite ca aport în natur&#259;, num&#259;rul de <span\nclass=SpellE>ac&#355;iuni</span> acordate pentru acestea <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\nnumele sau, dup&#259; caz, denumirea persoanei care le-a adus ca aport;</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1905557236\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2532\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1905557236\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>f)num&#259;rul <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> valoarea\nnominal&#259; a <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iunilor</span>;</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2140665331\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2531\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2140665331\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>f<sup>1</sup>)dac&#259; sunt mai multe categorii de <span\nclass=SpellE>ac&#355;iuni</span>, num&#259;rul, valoarea nominal&#259; <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> drepturile conferite fiec&#259;rei categorii de <span\nclass=SpellE>ac&#355;iuni</span>;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1618120301\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2530\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1618120301\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>f<sup>2</sup>)tipul <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>,\nrespectiv închis sau deschis, precum <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> orice <span\nclass=SpellE>restric&#355;ie</span> cu privire la transferul de <span\nclass=SpellE>ac&#355;iuni</span>;</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_198429499\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2529\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_198429499\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>g)datele de identificare a primilor membri ai consiliului\nde <span class=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span>, respectiv a primilor membri ai\nconsiliului de supraveghere;</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1590846492\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2528\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1590846492\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>g<sup>1</sup>)puterile conferite administratorilor <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span>, dup&#259; caz, directorilor, respectiv membrilor\ndirectoratului, <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> dac&#259; ei urmeaz&#259;\ns&#259; le exercite împreun&#259; sau separat;</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1859633005\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2527\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1859633005\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>h)datele de identificare a primilor cenzori sau a primului\nauditor financiar;</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_676324012\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2526\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_676324012\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>i)clauze privind conducerea, administrarea, <span\nclass=SpellE>func&#355;ionarea</span> <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\ncontrolul gestiunii <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> de\nc&#259;tre organele statutare, num&#259;rul membrilor consiliului de <span\nclass=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span> sau modul de stabilire a acestui\nnum&#259;r;</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_38873790\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2525\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_38873790\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>i<sup>1</sup>)[textul din Art. 8, litera I^1. din titlul\nII, capitolul I a fost abrogat la 17-apr-2009 de </span><span style='color:\n#1B1B1B'>Art. 1, punctul 1. din <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>Legea</i>\n88/2009</span><span style='color:black'>]</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>j)durata\n<span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>k)modul\nde distribuire a beneficiilor <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> de suportare a\npierderilor;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1125893661\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2524\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1125893661\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>k<sup>1</sup>)</span><s><span style='color:#E51C23'>dup&#259;\ncaz, datele de identificare a beneficiarilor reali <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\na <span class=SpellE>modalit&#259;&#355;ilor</span> în care se exercit&#259;\ncontrolul asupra <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>;</span></s><br>\n<br>\n<u><span style='color:#569748'>[textul din Art. 8, litera K^1. din titlul II,\ncapitolul I a fost abrogat la 06-dec-2024 de Art. 1, punctul 2. din <i\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>Legea</i> 299/2024]</span></u></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>l)sediile\nsecundare - sucursale, <span class=SpellE>agen&#355;ii</span>, <span\nclass=SpellE>reprezentan&#355;e</span> sau alte asemenea <span class=SpellE>unit&#259;&#355;i</span>\nf&#259;r&#259; personalitate juridic&#259; -, atunci când se <span\nclass=SpellE>înfiin&#355;eaz&#259;</span> o dat&#259; cu societatea, sau <span\nclass=SpellE>condi&#355;iile</span> pentru <span class=SpellE>înfiin&#355;area</span>\nlor ulterioar&#259;, dac&#259; se are în vedere o atare <span class=SpellE>înfiin&#355;are</span>;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_979552227\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2523\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_979552227\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>m)orice avantaj special acordat, în momentul <span\nclass=SpellE>înfiin&#355;&#259;rii</span> <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>\nsau pân&#259; în momentul în care societatea este autorizat&#259; s&#259; <span\nclass=SpellE>î&#351;i</span> înceap&#259; activitatea, oric&#259;rei persoane\ncare a participat la constituirea <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>\nori la <span class=SpellE>tranzac&#355;ii</span> conducând la acordarea <span\nclass=SpellE>autoriza&#355;iei</span> în cauz&#259;, precum <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\nidentitatea beneficiarilor unor astfel de avantaje;</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_862046473\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2522\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_862046473\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>n)num&#259;rul <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iunilor</span>\ncomanditarilor în societatea în comandit&#259; pe <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iuni</span>;</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_516738692\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2521\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_516738692\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>o)cuantumul total sau cel <span class=SpellE>pu&#355;in</span>\nestimativ al tuturor cheltuielilor pentru constituire;</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>p)modul\nde dizolvare <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> de lichidare a <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>.</span></p>"}